description: Welcome home to this light-filled and inviting studio residence in the Seaport's desirable FP3 building! With stunning contemporary finishes, large windows, and high ceilings, this home caters to a luxurious lifestyle in one of Boston’s hottest neighborhoods. This spacious studio loft boasts a state-of-the-art kitchen with stainless steel appliances and sleek Arclinea cabinetry, a large foyer, custom walk-in closet, in-unit laundry, and hardwood floors throughout. In addition to the magnificent in-unit amenities, FP3 also offers a common roof deck, rotating art gallery, 24-hour concierge and staff, and professional management. Just a short distance to Boston's Seaport District, Financial District and South Station.
